Build a full-stack web application called “AI-Assisted Smart Content Blog Platform”.

🎯 Core Objective:
Create a blogging platform that automatically generates high-quality, SEO-friendly blog posts based on trending topics using AI. The system must focus on content quality, structured writing, and user readability instead of spam-like automation.

---

🧠 Backend Requirements (Node.js + Express):

1. Implement a cron job using node-cron that runs every 4 hours:
   - Fetch trending topics from a news API (or mock data)
   - Filter topics (remove duplicates, avoid generic topics, prioritize niche + trending topics)

2. Integrate Gemini API for content generation:
   - Generate blog posts with:
     - Title
     - Introduction
     - H2 and H3 headings
     - Detailed explanation
     - Actionable insights
     - FAQ section
   - Ensure human-like, non-repetitive, and helpful tone

3. Post-processing:
   - Generate SEO metadata (meta title, description)
   - Create URL slug
   - Clean formatting (Markdown or HTML)

4. Image Integration:
   - Fetch relevant images using Unsplash API based on blog keywords
   - Add image URL and alt text to blog
   - Optionally support AI-generated images

5. Database (MongoDB):
   - Blog schema:
     - title
     - slug
     - content
     - image
     - tags
     - metaTitle
     - metaDescription
     - status (draft/published)
     - createdAt

6. API Endpoints:
   - GET /blogs → list blogs
   - GET /blogs/:slug → single blog
   - POST /generate → trigger blog generation manually
   - PATCH /blogs/:id → update status (draft/publish)

---

🎨 Frontend Requirements (Next.js + Tailwind CSS):

⚠️ IMPORTANT: Design must be MOBILE-FIRST and fully responsive.

1. Pages:
   - Home Page (list of blogs)
   - Blog Detail Page
   - Admin Dashboard (optional)

2. UI Design Guidelines:
   - Clean, modern, minimal design
   - Mobile-first layout (optimize for small screens first)
   - Use responsive grid and flexbox
   - Smooth typography and spacing
   - Sticky header with navigation
   - Card-based blog layout

3. Home Page:
   - Blog cards with:
     - Image
     - Title
     - Short description
     - Read more button
   - Responsive grid:
     - 1 column (mobile)
     - 2 columns (tablet)
     - 3 columns (desktop)

4. Blog Page:
   - Hero image
   - Title + metadata
   - Well-formatted content (headings, paragraphs, spacing)
   - Inline images between sections
   - FAQ section styling

5. Admin Dashboard:
   - List of generated blogs
   - Status toggle (draft/published)
   - Preview option

---

📱 Mobile Responsiveness (VERY IMPORTANT):
- Use Tailwind responsive utilities (sm, md, lg)
- Optimize font sizes and spacing for small screens
- Ensure touch-friendly buttons
- Avoid overflow issues
- Lazy load images for performance

---

⚡ Additional Features:
- Loading states (skeleton UI)
- Error handling
- SEO optimization (meta tags, structured content)
- Clean code structure (modular components and services)

---

🧩 Tech Stack:
- Frontend: Next.js + Tailwind CSS
- Backend: Node.js + Express
- Database: MongoDB
- AI: Gemini API
- Image API: Unsplash

